descriptionHtml:
[color=#ffff00]Windbringer[/color] Eng/Rus v1.0

[color=#ffff00]Author[/color]: Ronnie Magnum
[color=#ffff00]Requirements[/color]: Skyrim

This mod adds a new sword - Windbringer - that can be obtained on a small island East from Solitude. This weapon have no enchantment and can be improved with a quicksilver ingot.
